label: ham
subject: [R] Gini coefficient in R
body: 86 (return) [ _Ubi lapsus! Quid feci?_ a motto which was probably adopted by the Powderham branch, after the loss of the earldom of Devonshire, &c. The primitive arms of the Courtenays were, _Or_, _three torteaux_, _Gules_, which seem to denote their affinity with Godfrey of Bouillon, and the ancient counts of Boulogne.]
